    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 2.5",
    "body" : "<p>What kind of problem do you get with <a href=\"http://jregex.sourceforge.net/\" rel=\"nofollow\">jregex</a>?\nIt worked well for me under java5 and java6.</p>\n\n<p>Jregex does the job well (even if the last version is from 2002), unless <a href=\"http://download.oracle.com/javase/7/docs/api/java/util/regex/Pattern.html#groupname\" rel=\"nofollow\">you want to wait for javaSE 7</a>.</p>\n"
