    "body" : "<p>For people coming to this late: Java 7 adds named groups. <a href=\"http://download.oracle.com/javase/7/docs/api/java/util/regex/Matcher.html#group%28java.lang.String%29\">Matcher.group(String groupName) documentation.</a></p>\n"
