      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
      "body" : "I am very interested in the joni option mentioned by Ryan above -- do you have any code snippets using named capture groups - I have managed to get basic matching and searching to work correctly - but I don&#39;t see which method I would use to get access to the groupNames or to get a capture&#39;s value using the group name."
