    "score" : 2,
    "last_activity_date" : 1338115324,
    "creation_date" : 1338115324,
    "answer_id" : 10773333,
    "question_id" : 415580,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>For those running pre-java7, named groups are supported by <a href=\"https://github.com/jruby/joni\" rel=\"nofollow\">joni</a> (Java port of the <a href=\"http://www.geocities.jp/kosako3/oniguruma/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Oniguruma</a> regexp library).  Documentation is sparse, but it has worked well for us.<br>\nBinaries are available via Maven (<a href=\"http://repository.codehaus.org/org/jruby/joni/joni/\" rel=\"nofollow\">http://repository.codehaus.org/org/jruby/joni/joni/</a>).</p>\n"
